<table><tr><td>Roberts KB, Younes A, Hodgson DC, Advani R, Dabaja BS, Dhakal S, Flowers CR, Ha CS, Hoppe BS, Mendenhall NP, Metzger ML, Plastaras JP, Shapiro R, Smith SM, Terezakis SA, Winkfield KM, Constine LS, Expert Panel on Radiation Oncology–Lymphoma. ACR Appropriateness Criteria® Hodgkin lymphoma - unfavorable clinical stage I and II. Reston (VA): American College of Radiology (ACR); 2015. 22 p.  [83 references]</td></tr></table>                    <p><a href="/web/20180713041356/https://www.guideline.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=49926&amp;contentType=fulltextlink&amp;redirect=https%253a%252f%252facsearch.acr.org%252fdocs%252f69389%252fNarrative">View the original guideline documentation</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180713041356im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/></p>
